Poster composition
think about what goes where
Before creating your poster, think about what goes where on the poster and with what purpose.
Also think about the context where you will be using the poster: will it be accompanied with speech or will it have to be self explanatory
Could you add icons to boost your message?
Or remove elements to simplify message?
